summary: A Hunting camp in Riverwood. Lots of Storage, and mannequins male and female. Easy design with shield racks to decorate. Pool and many interations npcs can use. Targets out back.
descriptionHtml:
V4- DRAGON EYE LODGE

Had to basically recopy the home, and reset a lot. But finally got a good working mod here. Hopefully no more Mannequin problems. If you are experiencing issues, keep reading. I do not have any issues with anything, so hopefully neither will you.

BUGS:
None no more floating mannequins, no  more issues. This should be a good working set up now. If there is an issue, it maybe conflicting with another mod.

REQUIRMENTS:
DawnGuard
Hearthfires
Dragonborn
Sandraniks Pretty mannequins-I  would recommend using as it was what i had to use for the male and female mannequins.

COC aaalodgev4
use the key in the Delphine\'s room, on the table.

Pics are older versions but give a somewhat layout of the home.


Check out my other mods:

Dragons Eye Manor: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28232

Trybesman: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29326
